Package: rrricanes
Type: Package
Title: Web scraper for Atlantic and east Pacific hurricanes and tropical storms
Description: Get archived data of past and current hurricanes and tropical 
  storms for the Atlantic and eastern Pacific oceans. Data is available for 
  storms since 1998.
Version: 0.2.0-5
Authors@R: c(person("Tim", "Trice", email = "tim.trice@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Tim Trice <tim.trice@gmail.com>
Depends:
  R (>= 3.3.3)
URL: https://github.com/timtrice/rrricanes
BugReports: https://github.com/timtrice/rrricanes/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
